    <item>
      <title>拜登抨击万斯，称他谈论“关于劳动人民的大事”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/biden-hits-vance-says-he-talks-big-game-about-working-people</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登严厉批评唐纳德·特朗普选择 JD 万斯作为竞选搭档，并预示民主党将通过质疑这位俄亥俄州参议员的独立性和民粹主义资历来向选民展示他的个性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/biden-hits-vance-says-he-talks-big-game-about-working-people</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 20:15:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州反对 ESG，贝莱德聘请政府联络员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/blackrock-hires-government-liaison-as-texas-pushes-against-esg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了抵御来自德克萨斯州共和党的批评，贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 正在奥斯汀招聘一名新员工，以加强其政府关系人员的队伍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/blackrock-hires-government-liaison-as-texas-pushes-against-esg</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>各州将以大衰退以来最快的速度削减支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/states-to-slash-spending-at-fastest-pace-since-great-recession</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计美国各州将削减预算，标志着经过多年刺激增长和减税政策推动后，各州的支出将回归更为温和的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/states-to-slash-spending-at-fastest-pace-since-great-recession</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>枪击事件发生后，特勤局加强对拜登和特朗普的保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/secret-service-beefing-up-biden-trump-protection-post-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员表示，在前总统遭遇暗杀后，美国特勤局加强了对总统乔·拜登、副总统卡马拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普的安保力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/secret-service-beefing-up-biden-trump-protection-post-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:27:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前特朗普特使理查德·格雷内尔支持乌克兰自治区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/ex-trump-envoy-grenell-advocates-autonomous-zones-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位可能在第二任期内担任重要职位的前特朗普政府大使主张与乌克兰达成和平协议，并表示该协议将保留该国领土，但允许设立自治区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/ex-trump-envoy-grenell-advocates-autonomous-zones-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:21:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命万斯为竞选搭档，挑选民粹主义门徒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-taps-rising-republican-star-jd-vance-as-running-mate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 任命 JD 万斯 (JD Vance) 为其竞选搭档，将这位风险投资家出身的参议员提拔为共和党总统候选人，他对民粹主义政治的拥护引起了全国的关注，并让他成为党内一颗冉冉升起的新星。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-taps-rising-republican-star-jd-vance-as-running-mate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍勃·梅内德斯陪审团询问是否需要一致同意才能宣告无罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/bob-menendez-jury-asks-judge-whether-unanimity-needed-to-acquit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，美国参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯腐败案的陪审员询问法官，是否必须一致同意才能对任何罪名作出无罪宣判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/bob-menendez-jury-asks-judge-whether-unanimity-needed-to-acquit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯·格里芬加入 GoFundMe 的捐助者行列，为特朗普袭击事件的受害者筹款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-campaign-gofundme-for-victims-of-attack-raises-3-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普竞选团队发起了一项 GoFundMe 活动，旨在帮助周六晚间疑似暗杀事件的受害者及其家属，目前该活动已从 56,000 多笔捐款中筹集到超过 430 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-campaign-gofundme-for-victims-of-attack-raises-3-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:49:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件后，共和党全国代表大会继续进行：值得关注的事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/rnc-2024-still-on-trump-shooting-impact-and-key-topics-speakers-to-watch-for</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管针对前总统唐纳德·特朗普的暗杀企图很可能成为 2024 年竞选活动中最重要的时刻之一，但密尔沃基共和党全国代表大会仍将如期举行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/rnc-2024-still-on-trump-shooting-impact-and-key-topics-speakers-to-watch-for</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
